}
```

## CDN Integration
Configure a CDN for static assets:

```typescript
export default defineConfig({
  performance: {
    cdn: {
      enabled: true,
      provider: 'cloudflare',
      domain: 'cdn.myapp.com',
      cacheControl: 'public, max-age=31536000',
    },
  },
});
```
